item.dc:creator: @LeScape LeScape
item.description:
@LeScape wrote:

Errors are located at:
client.java, line 1661 (problem with AttackNPC)
client.java, line 13457 (problem with process)
PlayerHandler.java, line 283 (problem with process)
process.java, line 23 (problem with run)

The problems are most likely methods or statements.
Learn to read your compiler instead of posting “omgwtf” as soon as something happens.

Oh, and most likely the problem is in only one line (I’m guessing PlayerHandler’s line) and that line references all of the other lines which is why they’re all erroring.
